snippet.title: GUITARS AND ROSES?!?  - Miraculous Ladybug S1 E21 and 22 REACTION - Zamber Reacts
snippet.description:
What does a Guitar and a Princess have in common?
They both appear in this episode :P


Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir Season 1 Episode 21 : " Guitar Villain "
Summary: Jagged Stone goes to extreme lengths when he can't tolerate the provocations of an arrogant young singer called Mr XY.

Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir Season 1 Episode 22 : " Princess Fragrance "
Summary: A fellow student of Marinette's gets akumatised by Hawk Moth. Now Princess Fragrance, she wants to abduct a prince visiting Paris. This new villain smells like trouble for Ladybug and Cat Noir.
